me.taylorkelly.mywarp.util.teleport

Class StrategicTeleportHandler

  • java.lang.Object
    • me.taylorkelly.mywarp.util.teleport.StrategicTeleportHandler
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    TeleportHandler

    public class StrategicTeleportHandler
extends java.lang.Object
implements TeleportHandler
    Parses teleport positions against a PositionValidationStrategy. If a valid position exists, the entity is teleported there. If no valid position exists, the teleport is canceled.
